# Template:
# Simplify the following expression
#
#    a x^2 y^2 + b x y  + c x y^2
#    ----------------------
#           d x y 
#
#
# We specify the answer first, and then just multiply it by d 
# so that all the numbers work out nicely. Everything is integer.
#
